OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774433137
OL,3,CKent meningitis survivor appears in
OL,4,Cfirst TV interview since ordeal
OL,6,FKent meningitis survivor Keeleigh
OL,7,FGoodwin speaks to Good Morning Britain
OL,8,Fin her first television interview
OL,9,Fsince spending a week in hospital with
OL,10,Fthe life-threatening illness.
OL,12,FKeeleigh Goodwin, aged 21, was rushed
OL,13,Fto hospital just days after a night
OL,14,Fout with friends in Canterbury's Club
OL,15,FChemistry.
OL,17,FThe nightclub was later linked to an
OL,18,Foutbreak of meningitis B, which she
OL,19,Fwas diagnosed with.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
