FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774433137
OL,3,CKent meningitis survivor appears in
OL,4,Cfirst TV interview since ordeal
OL,6,FKent saw 34 confirmed cases in the
OL,7,Farea, and the deaths of two young
OL,8,Fpeople, a university student and a
OL,9,Fsixth former.
OL,11,FAfter a week in hospital with the life-
OL,12,Fthreatening illness, Keeleigh joined
OL,13,FEd Balls and Susanna Reid on Good
OL,14,FMorning Britain on Tuesday morning,
OL,15,Fvia video link from her home.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774433137
OL,3,CKent meningitis survivor appears in
OL,4,Cfirst TV interview since ordeal
OL,6,FShe sat alongside her mum, Khali
OL,7,FGoodwin, who called on the Health
OL,8,FSecretary to get the Meningitis B
OL,9,Fvaccine rolled out to those who have
OL,10,Fmissed it, adding that "you can put a
OL,11,Fprice on life".
OL,13,FIn the interview, Keeleigh described
OL,14,Fher symptoms, saying she was in "a lot
OL,15,Fof pain", feeling achy all over with a
OL,16,Fsevere headache, before collapsing and
OL,17,Fhaving a seizure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
