PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774433137
OL,3,CKent meningitis survivor appears in
OL,4,Cfirst TV interview since ordeal
OL,6,FKeeleigh had been on a night out at
OL,7,Fthe venue on Thursday 12 March, with
OL,8,Fher symptoms progressing severely over
OL,9,Fthe following 30 hours.
OL,11,FSymptoms of meningitis can look
OL,12,Fsimilar to common illnesses like a
OL,13,Fcold or hangover, however, someone
OL,14,Fwith meningitis will usually become
OL,15,Fseriously ill in a matter of hours.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
