OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774433137
OL,3,CKent meningitis survivor appears in
OL,4,Cfirst TV interview since ordeal
OL,6,FSymptoms can include fever, seizures,
OL,7,Fvomiting, headache, a stiff neck, or a
OL,8,Frash that does not fade when a glass
OL,9,Fis pressed against it. Some people may
OL,10,Falso become drowsy, unresponsive or
OL,11,Fsensitive to bright lights.
OL,13,FThese symptoms can appear in any order
OL,14,Fand may not always be present at once.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
