PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774433137
OL,3,CKent meningitis survivor appears in
OL,4,Cfirst TV interview since ordeal
OL,6,FSome groups of meningococcal disease
OL,7,Fcan be prevented by vaccines, of which
OL,8,Fthere are multiple available in the UK.
OL,10,FKhali said that she believed that
OL,11,FKeeleigh had already been "completely
OL,12,Fvaccinated" so it was a "complete and
OL,13,Futter shock" to find out she had the
OL,14,Fillness.
OL,16,FThe MenB jab specifically offers
OL,17,Fprotection against meningococcal group
OL,18,FB bacteria, which is the strain of
OL,19,Fmeningitis that has caused the recent
OL,20,Foutbreak.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774433137
OL,3,CKent meningitis survivor appears in
OL,4,Cfirst TV interview since ordeal
OL,6,FHowever, the majority of young people
OL,7,Fborn before 2015 are not protected
OL,8,Fagainst meningitis B unless they have
OL,9,Fhad the jab privately, as it was
OL,10,Fintroduced on the NHS for babies in
OL,11,F2015.
OL,13,FThis is despite young people being one
OL,14,Fof the most at-risk groups of
OL,15,Fmeningitis.
OL,17,FThe MenB vaccine is offered on the NHS
OL,18,Ffor babies aged eight weeks, followed
OL,19,Fby a second dose at 12 weeks and a
OL,20,Fbooster at one year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774433137
OL,3,CKent meningitis survivor appears in
OL,4,Cfirst TV interview since ordeal
OL,6,FKhali urged Health Secretary Wes
OL,7,FStreeting to "get this vaccine rolled
OL,8,Fout to the people who missed it, cost
OL,9,Feffective or not", adding that "you
OL,10,Fcan put a price on life".
OL,12,FThe vaccine is currently being offered
OL,13,Fto people who could be linked to the
OL,14,Foutbreak, including some Year 11
OL,15,Fpupils, and has already been
OL,16,Fadministered to 600 people on the
OL,17,Funiversity campus.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
