FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774433137
OL,3,CKent meningitis survivor appears in
OL,4,Cfirst TV interview since ordeal
OL,6,FKeeleigh is eligible for the vaccine,
OL,7,Fbut says she has to be "well enough"
OL,8,Fto queue hours to receive it, adding
OL,9,Fthat she is "not strong enough to do
OL,10,Fthat yet".
OL,12,F"I was shocked that she would have to
OL,13,Fstand and wait for so long", her mum
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,FKeeleigh says she called 111 and was
OL,17,Ftold by her GP she would have to stand
OL,18,Fand queue like everybody else.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
